title: Wells Brothers Bar and Grill
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant and bar with marked vegetarian items including hummus, spinach artichoke dip, nachos, salads, and sandwiches. Build-your-own burger can be made with vegan garden burger with choice of toppings. Vegetarian items listed as possibly containing dairy and/or egg - ask.
